text: Ali Bani Hashemi (born 5 April 1934) is an Iranian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman bantamweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:Iranian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Iran Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tehran
